dc_description_s: This point data layer represents PLSS for Chippewa County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Chippewa_PLSS_2018.gdb
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
